{"tid":2513988,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中東籍男生被控8.31半周年暴動罪成 續還押至5月24日判刑","createTime":"2021-05-03T03:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T03:48:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8196bde4c3dce528c374dc7f715259a33cdfafb1","tid":2513988,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:24:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15383&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtVLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=97893d0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15383</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第卅二庭<br />\n#姚勳智法官 #聆取對控罪的回答<br />\n#20200229旺角 #831半週年<br />\n👤鈕 (19)🛑已還押逾14個月🛑<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：暴動<br />\n被告被控於2020年2月29日，在旺角西洋菜南街近豉油街一帶參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n控罪2：襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n被告被控於同日，在奶路臣街近彌敦道交界處襲擊正當執行職務的警員34731。<br />\n=================<br />\n‼️被告正式在庭上承認「暴動」罪，因認罪協議，「襲警」罪會存檔法庭‼️<br />\n=================<br />\n法庭把案件押後至2021年5月24日 10:00 進行判刑，期間被告人需繼續還押看管，法庭會為被告索取背景報告，若控辯雙方希望呈上案例予法庭參考，需於5月17日前呈上法庭。"},{"pid":"55a227026fd5b5a2ee613558d55521c7b1463b05","tid":2513988,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8395780c4c35f7d10b7fd12daffaae80e6f30c9d","tid":2513988,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5d222dd358badb31ef8997d0cf0b9f583da10c","tid":2513988,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow=/802x498/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow%3D%2F802x498%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif&h=108d9f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.31半周年有便衣警落單在旺角遭「私了」，一度拔槍自保，到場增援的防暴警拘捕一名外籍VTC學生，指他向警員投擲水樽和用竹枝指向警員。<br />\n<br />\n控罪書上顯示被告是「中東籍」，他被控於2020月年2月29日在奶路臣街近彌敦道交界襲擊警員A。<br />\n<br />\n被告毋須答辯，本案押後待警方撿取案發現場的閉路電視片段、為目擊證人錄取口供，及索取警員A的醫療報告等。主任裁判官羅德泉拒絕被告保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtVLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=f2ffd345\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&h=598fe943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/</a>"},{"pid":"be03ab4910a5bc7e74e1ab1888463a4fab29a4c4","tid":2513988,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f204678a8e0f097a35c8d99cb4a39b4a513c3510","tid":2513988,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a98553794e8dec128082da85e9041b60c23a0bf","tid":2513988,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:33:54.000Z","msg":"扔個水樽就暴動，唉"},{"pid":"40e982744150848761025e74c4b6104e8f1d871b","tid":2513988,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f5d222dd358badb31ef8997d0cf0b9f583da10c","tid":2513988,"uid":240362,"l